{"tid":2346451,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周柏豪龜縮缺席商台叱咤 今現身新城頒獎禮奪兩豬肉獎","createTime":"2020-12-30T09:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T19:42:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c90cf41fd5713280c100bf6f6d50a53f4ae811b2","tid":2346451,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T09:18:57.000Z","msg":"周：最緊要屋企人平安<br />\n周柏豪對商台的頒獎禮避之則吉，不過對沒有太多政治包袱的新城頒獎禮卻無任歡迎。今日下午3點，周柏豪現身葵涌工業大廈的頒獎禮現場，而今次亦是他表忠後第一次現身。現場傳媒嘗試叫停他做訪問，不過記者越嗌他越走，未有停低，之後他對着眾人微笑及揮一揮手，便直上工業大廈。而他最後憑歌曲《劫後餘生》奪勁爆歌曲及奪得勁爆男歌手奬兩個「份量」十足的獎項，好威威！<br />\n<br />\n他領獎時先多謝公司和fans，之後似有感而發說：「做咩都好，最緊要係屋企人開心平安，冇嘢重要得過呢樣嘢！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201230/XRPCJH7KTZGNBCTEKYOCQVBBVI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201230%2FXRPCJH7KTZGNBCTEKYOCQVBBVI%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSHO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=77da1434\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201230%2FXRPCJH7KTZGNBCTEKYOCQVBBVI%2F&h=033da2cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201230/XRPCJH7KTZGNBCTEKYOCQVBBVI/</a>"},{"pid":"0e47b4a2226b1237afebd8fc647f1335884a27f8","tid":2346451,"uid":239270,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"冇得返轉頭，最弊2面不是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3873a27a35fdcaa1dc43fafa83152585e56a832e","tid":2346451,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0e47b4a2226b1237afebd8fc647f1335884a27f8","tid":2346451,"uid":239270,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"冇得返轉頭，最弊2面不是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T09:28:45.000Z","msg":"佢自己攞嚟衰"},{